name: Strange Part
desc:
A strange mechanical part obtained near Merusea Village. It looks subtly different from common mechanical parts.

You have no idea why it ended up here, but beautiful metal products like this are loved by Melusines...

value.text:
World Quests - 'A Brush of Seafoam and Crimson', '"Hey, This Isn't Pumpkin Soup..."', 'Book of Esoteric Revelations', 'Echoes of the Ancient World', 'Fishing Game', 'The Lone Phantom Sail', 'Strange Stone Chronicle (Part 2)', 'The Three Primary Colors of the Solar Corona'
World Quest - 'There Will Come Soft Rains'
Specific chests in Elynas
Interact with Serene after completing 'A Brush of Seafoam and Crimson' and 'Blue Longing of Heart and Moon'
